{"tid":1465600,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"梁天琦：請不要被仇恨支配自己","createTime":"2019-08-13T16:11:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T07:44:37.000Z","uid":207258,"like":356,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":118,"replies":[{"pid":"f8560346183142517962748ad93b8a486e0212a8","tid":1465600,"uid":207258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:11:25.000Z","msg":"如果我哋再係咁落去就只會同共產黨無分別<br />\n與野獸作鬥的人 要小心自己也變成野獸<br />\n請各位巴打做任何事之前要冷靜 三思啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13715becfe51f6946188a94808a333e605f53208","tid":1465600,"uid":207258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:11:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11726c373e70a94ba493129707a7de5813c3f67a","tid":1465600,"uid":207258,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:12:59.000Z","msg":"如果搞出人命就只會比藉口中國㗎咋"},{"pid":"0d3c5d87a7a66e0cfadd709336ba5b9096d137a3","tid":1465600,"uid":207258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:13:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf45939652748526bd9e3f6f46747fa235df4d77","tid":1465600,"uid":86592,"like":3,"dislike":9,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:13:42.000Z","msg":"勸唔到了，回不了頭"},{"pid":"1ed072522292eea8b60783c7f671c51abc1713ac","tid":1465600,"uid":22407,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:13:56.000Z","msg":"希望大家想想天琦嘅說話<br />\n勿忘初衷 記住我地爭取緊嘅係咩<br />\n唔好俾狗打亂我地 有鬼唔第一日嘅事<br />\n唔好俾仇恨蒙蔽理智<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n<br />\n不篤灰 不割𥱊 不分化"},{"pid":"4b035837d9ac563d03385c6b9a814312ed06103b","tid":1465600,"uid":207258,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:14:06.000Z","msg":"我明大家都好嬲 但唔好盲目啊"},{"pid":"5ccb085d7122695827f67b68b7adbfd03097e511","tid":1465600,"uid":31637,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:14:20.000Z","msg":"比藉口中國做咩? 出兵? 出兵咪返屋企訓覺囉, 等佢地放工先再滅佢地囉"},{"pid":"df425a51834690b1e17d8a6a9775fbae013813f9","tid":1465600,"uid":207258,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:17:44.000Z","msg":"如果我哋連基本人道救援都唔比 咁同班警犬 共產黨有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />香港人勝在理智文明啊"},{"pid":"2083f3d89437e92a216f34ef1875df3d0107a05f","tid":1465600,"uid":60000,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:18:11.000Z","msg":"所以要支持政府決定"},{"pid":"44abb2759c28c0d74c81ce61a7f5f6106f7998aa","tid":1465600,"uid":31542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:18:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0c0d980e2a0b38714b0a0215b1da7dccbc365f47","tid":1465600,"uid":121270,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:18:41.000Z","msg":"前線好情緒化 連first aid都屌 冷靜少少好冇"},{"pid":"b06f3a2627b137dea4fd5a830c3aaca4be500563","tid":1465600,"uid":245484,"like":1,"dislike":17,"score":-16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:18:49.000Z","msg":"食撚夠梁天琦人血饅頭未啊屌你老母"},{"pid":"c006d8343b71a978fc905d41df50d5d800f1d65c","tid":1465600,"uid":180595,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:19:40.000Z","msg":"清醒的人唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0aee8001e528b8a740dcfa70f3a49338b894c76c","tid":1465600,"uid":25866,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:20:14.000Z","msg":"核彈都不割.打錯人都唔割. 就算你打錯我都唔會割<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"559c2f1857a78feed4993512b737dc611c5a0a9e","tid":1465600,"uid":119623,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:20:37.000Z","msg":"所有香港人都好嬲，我都好想啲仆街死，但不停同自己講唔好被仇恨沖昏頭腦。我地目標唔淨止係佢，各位真係要冷靜啲，有排打㗎呢場仗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果唔冷靜落去我地同啲仆街無分別㗎咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1a902c2cd8983c4822cf96237dfdf02b80763c5","tid":1465600,"uid":218731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:20:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ea41446427c14b163d97cb6d453e745632a27cdc","tid":1465600,"uid":273495,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:21:03.000Z","msg":"講真條友你都挷住左，仲幾個人踢佢過左火⋯<br />\n警察都識係鏡頭外打，鏡頭前點都會扮哂野<br />\n我地要輿論架，外國既香港既都要架<br />\n之前打人都話有理由因爲佢打人先，但今次？<br />\n因為有件衫就打人，白衣紅衣都係見黑衫就打架<br />\n唔好變成你最憎恨既個種人"},{"pid":"2f382a3123f169ce3ce7d7984054f8b7134fbbfb","tid":1465600,"uid":299860,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:21:07.000Z","msg":"同意<br />\n<br />\n幫推<br />\n<br />\n不嬲唔打戰俘<br />\n<br />\n捉到就多一件證據<br />\n<br />\n一打就錯<br />\n<br />\n捉到再打多幾野同警有乜分別<br />\n<br />\n分明有人混入製造混亂<br />\n<br />\n你可以話我P牌冷氣軍師<br />\n<br />\n勇武並不是呢個時候"},{"pid":"dbeea49b3dd3bd193da39cf3caca47c1a29c83f8","tid":1465600,"uid":218731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:21:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f779e148652ade2d3beca6738f0ddefa4532fc7a","tid":1465600,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:21:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55025481d55b86c124cb2fb7f253bba02c8a6061","tid":1465600,"uid":218731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:22:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"df246882cabf94378ac2eae61eb7d4d175bf853b","tid":1465600,"uid":31542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:22:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8b5c75d103f6c25d4ec651a9c763168db8b234ad","tid":1465600,"uid":207258,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:23:44.000Z","msg":"千祈唔好一時之憤而失民意啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/