地唔係為左搞藍絲搞警察先進行兩個幾月既運動 千其唔好再做d不利己既野<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">絕不割蓆</span>"},{"pid":"7d4b1828c38879f215094632d3be87e024f55341","tid":1465600,"uid":66202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:26:05.000Z","msg":"今日太唔冷靜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c16e05cecc128a7c18a40160866fafc158a12412","tid":1465600,"uid":50437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:26:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b24eaad3b5368f2c808918c7035e61605b258e4","tid":1465600,"uid":199114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:26:21.000Z","msg":"香港差佬入一入嚟<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1465562\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1465562</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"acc2229c955ffdbec09db03a185aab7e2f653339","tid":1465600,"uid":43422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:26:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9cdfa501847cbf4fc6c879306ed62b992730814a","tid":1465600,"uid":67069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:26:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44510852296a249c07df7d979135c0bb8398995c","tid":1465600,"uid":185183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:27:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"751107a38c33b3fe9f9ded1b9e9a4a0a36192273","tid":1465600,"uid":234899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:27:01.000Z","msg":"Gg"},{"pid":"dc8696205d568e6be73bd808d508418d5f552a9c","tid":1465600,"uid":68822,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:27:06.000Z","msg":"機場一役喺要喺「公安」同「醫護第一」之間取決一方，從而比對家分化<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1465094/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1465094/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n對中共黎講犧牲一個公安<br />\n同收買一個金毛MK仔同收買啲人扮勇武掉野去警車唔係無可能<br />\n搵幾個人就挑起到你地內鬥<br />\n圍左公安咁耐有無得著？對五大訴求有無幫助？<br />\n唔喺幫個公安講說話，而喺處事要為大局著想<br />\n圍左三、四個鐘頭先上到醫護車<br />\n之後個金毛MK仔即刻第一時間沖出馬路靜坐阻路<br />\n我就覺得成年事好鬼鬼<br />\n根本喺一場中共/黑警Show<br />\n最大敵人根本就係你地自己<br />\n要時刻都有批判性思考<br />\n入得機場和理非就和理非<br />\n比中共睇穿你班人「好憎公安」同「讓路比醫護」兩者之間做出決定<br />\n萬死個公安死左就有位比人入<br />\n但就係咁比人分化你話抵唔抵？"},{"pid":"f2f2d63ab1c1bdf7479b45b85df4d24723027b89","tid":1465600,"uid":106071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:27:08.000Z","msg":"求下大家唔好比仇恨支配啊"},{"pid":"7aac4295131b8e4c6f2ab02f94b47a22c6eabfac","tid":1465600,"uid":89031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:27:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"654f8d31013db2cbe4e0d1d331f3fd2155913e27","tid":1465600,"uid":164482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:27:25.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2b271887a72a71d4462eafe4b44d8c1ecc783c48","tid":1465600,"uid":207258,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:27:34.000Z","msg":"我唔係督灰 割蓆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但大家真係要保持冷靜<br />\n巴絲們能夠撐到今日係因為我哋做啱每一步"},{"pid":"ac9e800a12783431e5760518ef7ddfd9dfbe96b0","tid":1465600,"uid":202961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:27:38.000Z","msg":"push，勇武都需要策略，唔好俾位人入"},{"pid":"81d232eae89a2420c3b81a8e9a3f39cad71bc7bf","tid":1465600,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:27:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"296e7af7ba2230d58311ac5c6e493a2fe291f945","tid":1465600,"uid":146243,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:27:49.000Z","msg":"係全世界記者鏡頭近距離影住都照郁手 first aid做緊野都仲想郁<br />\n<br />\n真係唔知係控制唔到情緒定特登"},