yTime":"2019-08-13T16:37:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5a38cc44b297b390e97e677e3bdd9f6412e58a86","tid":1465600,"uid":207258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c9cefd0b8e32bdd4fd9dc19c0324b8e3af67960","tid":1465600,"uid":188685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:35:23.000Z","msg":"今日連記者同救護都打....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:37:18.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過大家都係一時火遮眼啫 冇心嘅"},{"pid":"448f3c92f02cb828d9bffa583d07e583bbd50a67","tid":1465600,"uid":216178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:37:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0ddc3f3d067ebc8442515313c1636dd7a2b7c35","tid":1465600,"uid":67069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:37:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f40df25d29ae06ecb53666e9e1c87cfb25168cb9","tid":1465600,"uid":14087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:37:30.000Z","msg":"警世文 機場一戰之我見<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1465840\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1465840</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我地唔靠外國靠自己？</span>攬炒巴登報無？共和黨無？人權法無？侵侵無？澳洲無？聯合國無？人權組織無？如果無外國 一早派軍隊殺撚哂我地啦 <span style=\"color: red;\">我地個焦土係要靠外國架？無外國制裁我地一早死撚哂啦</span> 咪撚咁低能啦 你依家咁做未又係搞9旅客想等外國出聲，但咁搞無人會想幫我地 <span style=\"color: green;\">我想贏呀，唔想發左二個月夢白費呀屌</span><br />\n<br />\n咁你依家去夾住班旅客，唔俾佢地走，直至外國肯幫拖，<span style=\"color: red;\">咁你照下鏡，果一刻你係香港人，定係變成一個暴徒？</span>你真係覺得咁樣對個運動有幫助？平心而論，我唔該您<span style=\"color: green;\">跳出深黃框框用普通入角度去睇呢件事，外國唔係深黃，我地一直係自己個框框去睇，好難贏，我地要多角度思考，去就自己爭取最大既勝算</span><br />\n<br />\n依家係<span style=\"color: red;\">林鄭擺到明放人入機場帶頭搞事 想抹黑我地 點解我地要中計.</span>.. <span style=\"color: gold;\">我知我地點都唔割 我都係</span> 但<span style=\"color: green;\">對個運動毫無利益 </span>外國知道既資訊無我地自己人咁清楚 佢地只會覺得我地係搞事 你係機場衝，除左肉酸有乜撚野用，記唔記得點解我地去機場？係因為想宣揚我地個情況係全世界旅客知，我問你，我地依家似乜野？？？我地依家就係肉撚酸，連旅客都反感，咁<span style=\"color: green;\">我地當初去機場為乜呀？</span><br />\n<br />\n借問聲 咁樣連<span style=\"color: green;\">全世界遊客都對我地反感 我地仲係咪當初既香港人 為自由去爭取</span>？咁樣橫蠻無理法只會令我地<span style=\"color: red;\">立場惡化，對我地既抗爭有咩幫助</span>？機管局自己取消航班我地先叫有用，咁樣自己阻人上機 有咩意義？機管局會因為你阻住果幾個遊客而取消航班？個遊客未無辜硬食哂，再加<span style=\"color: red;\">傳媒抹黑，我地未輸哂囉 </span>，依家搞到我地變到神憎鬼厭咁 仲點樣贏 ?<span style=\"color: green;\">醒下啦，唔好俾憤怒沖昏頭腦，我地係要贏，唔係要發洩，咁搞對件事無幫助，琴日機管局警察咁搞，世界矛頭直指政府，但今日呢？直接我地呀，理智呀手足,我地要贏!!!!!!放下仇恨，智取，唔好俾林鄭得逞...機場戰線應該係繼續文宣和你飛好嗎， <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不分化不割席，但真係想贏，唔想一子錯滿盤階落索<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n記住我地香港人係點<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gLG04ac.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgLG04ac.png&h=fef1b4e1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7a35ea7aa95fba4b69c9c61c35c62779705a6570","tid":1465600,"uid":282249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:37:34.000Z","msg":"推啊"},{"pid":"8996e46196691ba1fdd30738a445416265c200c8","tid":1465600,"uid":280743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1ed072522292eea8b60783c7f671c51abc1713ac","tid":1465600,"uid":22407,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:13:56.000Z","msg":"希望大家想想天琦嘅說話<br />\n勿忘初衷 記住我地爭取緊嘅係咩<br />\n唔好俾狗打亂我地 有鬼唔第一日嘅事<br />\n唔好俾仇恨蒙蔽理智<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n<br />\n不篤灰 不割𥱊 不分化"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:37:42.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"aeab8ec2ff08ce2ff3a898e6f0c90a1e19a8e7da","tid":1465600,"uid":89546,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:37:42.000Z","msg":"天琦真係智者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21db792a63855fb968b57f34ec0e8e4e2d73f9f9","tid":1465600,"uid":108901,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:37:54.000Z","msg":"1. 唔可以打記者<br />\n2. 唔可以打救護人員<br />\n3. 唔可以係冇黑警情況下用雷射筆同電筒<br />\n4. 唔可以濫用酷刑<br />\n5. 唔可以攻擊一般平民"},{"pid":"8969f10f1cae99cb037ca9b52dd23c82c18fa59a","tid":1465600,"uid":282249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bdfcef7032435a98c59e3b4d461c567a83281179","tid":1465600,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f382a3123f169ce3ce7d7984054f8b7134fbbfb","tid":1465600,"uid":299860,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:21:07.000Z","msg":"同意<br />\n<br />\n幫推<br />\n<br />\n不嬲唔打戰俘<br />\n<br />\n捉到就多一件證據<br />\n<br />\n一打就錯<br />\n<br />\n捉到再打多幾野同警有乜分別<br />\n<br />\n分明有人混入製造混亂<br />\n<br />\n你可以話我P牌冷氣軍師<br />\n<br />\n勇武並不是呢個時候"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:28:01.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:38:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bd99ea121b7a914dd26986e4e7188a6faf9331cd","tid":1465600,"uid":38317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:38:16.000Z","msg":"真係要冷靜<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ccfc957edbfe1aa616ebb6f184654840a96bddc","tid":1465600,"uid":1915,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:38:22.000Z","msg":"咪拎住依句分化啦 乜鳩都賴落仇恨支配<br />\n佢講抗爭無底線你唔quote?"},{"pid":"e59d93ae4e072fbb276921ce992844d7e7de6e02","tid":1465600,"uid":282249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c9cefd0b8e32bdd4fd9dc19c0324b8e3af67960","tid":1465600,"uid":188685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:35:23.000Z","msg":"今日連記者同救護都打....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:38:31.000Z","msg":"唔好咁啦之後"},{"pid":"a240d4c367ff70a2996efddfae6566911f827967","tid":1465600,"uid":38317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"21db792a63855fb968b57f34ec0e8e4e2