仲點樣贏 ?<span style=\"color: green;\">醒下啦，唔好俾憤怒沖昏頭腦，我地係要贏，唔係要發洩，咁搞對件事無幫助，琴日機管局警察咁搞，世界矛頭直指政府，但今日呢？直接我地呀，理智呀手足,我地要贏!!!!!!放下仇恨，智取，唔好俾林鄭得逞...機場戰線應該係繼續文宣和你飛好嗎， <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不分化不割席，但真係想贏，唔想一子錯滿盤階落索<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n記住我地香港人係點<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gLG04ac.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgLG04ac.png&h=fef1b4e1&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:39:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d27403951b9eb75d26244dde1b5a9389466329f","tid":1465600,"uid":170014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:39:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3414cffd0c6cfcab7cc30512d0b447ac020ff702","tid":1465600,"uid":108901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:40:05.000Z","msg":"1. 唔可以打記者<br />\n2. 唔可以打救護人員<br />\n3. 唔可以係冇黑警情況下用雷射筆同電筒<br />\n4. 唔可以濫用酷刑<br />\n5. 唔可以攻擊一般平民"},{"pid":"68c78f987e438dd3093c99ed78a087c928fdc919","tid":1465600,"uid":61257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:40:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc1d5c77181a2c9adda2b765d9f36de64ea5cb3d","tid":1465600,"uid":13173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:40:37.000Z","msg":"屌你收撚皮好冇<br />\n<br />\n中國要做低你一早做咗啦<br />\n<br />\n中國做嘢洗諗藉口，佢要做，做撚完再同佢班國民洗腦都得啦，你都傻on9<br />\n<br />\n宜家中國唔係唔想做，而係唔敢做、做唔到<br />\n<br />\n呢班扮示威者嘅，畀啲教訓佢就啱，咪以為香港人唔會還手"},{"pid":"0700f955bc08fac2ea6903702661e0f30dab4425","tid":1465600,"uid":282249,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0ccfc957edbfe1aa616ebb6f184654840a96bddc","tid":1465600,"uid":1915,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:38:22.000Z","msg":"咪拎住依句分化啦 乜鳩都賴落仇恨支配<br />\n佢講抗爭無底線你唔quote?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:41:23.000Z","msg":"抗爭無